TITLE: Implementing Asynchronous Tool Specification in Java
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create an asynchronous tool specification for a basic calculator using the Model Context Protocol Java SDK. The specification includes a JSON schema for the tool's parameters and an asynchronous handler function to implement the tool's logic.
SOURCE: https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/modelcontextprotocol/blob/main/docs/sdk/java/mcp-server.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_9

