TITLE: Using Tools with Asynchronous MCP Client in Java
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to discover and execute server-side tools using the asynchronous MCP client API with reactive programming patterns. Shows listing tools and executing them with parameters in a non-blocking way.
