TITLE: Accessing Resources with MCP Java Client (Sync API)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to list available resources and retrieve resource content using the synchronous API of the MCP Java client. It shows listing resources and their names, as well as retrieving resource content using a URI template.
SOURCE: https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/modelcontextprotocol/blob/main/docs/sdk/java/mcp-client.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: java
