TITLE: Implementing Logging in MCP Server Tool (Java)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement logging support in an MCP server tool, including creating a tool specification that sends log messages using different severity levels and building a server with logging capabilities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/modelcontextprotocol/blob/main/docs/sdk/java/mcp-server.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_19

